data.description: Your search is over! This 2 bedroom 1 bath has been fully updated and has a very open floor plan. In the kitchen all the stainless steel appliances, butcher block and stackable washer and dryer will stay. The property has a new HVAC system and additional ductwork has been added.  You will love the oversized 3 car garage. There's an additional storage building to store your lawn equipment, bikes etc....All on over a half acre lot. Don't forget it's in popular Haysville school district!! Plenty of shopping and restaurant's near by and easy access to the Kansas turnpike or highway. Hurry schedule your showing today!
